2. [discipline:default] [feedback/gitignore-write-guardrail]
   Any code, scripts, or agents modifying `.gitignore` must NOT add `.gm/rs-learn.db` or `.code-search/` to ignore rules. If a legacy stray `rs-learn.db` at repo root is found, migrate it to `.gm/rs-learn.db` rather than ignoring. `lib/template-builder.js::generateGitignore()` is the canonical emitter for downstream repos and correctly omits `.gm/` and `.code-search/` lines by design.
